longBusinessSummary: HD View 360, Inc. provides security surveillance products and systems to commercial users under the HD View 360 brand name in the United States. Its products include IP network video recorders, analog digital video recorders, HDCVI video recorders, HDCVI cameras, HDCVI pan tilt cameras, IP cameras, IP pan tilt zoom cameras, video IP intercoms, analog cameras, connectors, cables, secure lock boxes, HDMI video products, and IP networking products, as well as tools, testers, and power supplies. The company also provides various services, such as networking, IT solutions, structured cabling, mobile app and mobile device integration, and closed-circuit television installation and upgrades. HD View 360, Inc. was founded in 2014 and is based in Miami, Florida.
